# This file is kept for reference. The actual models are split per product:
#
#   platform/model.fga    — shared types (user, tenant, platform, product, document)
#   marketplace/model.fga — marketplace-specific types (store, order, product_listing, etc.)
#
# Each product gets its own OpenFGA store. To add a new product:
#   1. Create a new directory: openfga/{product-name}/model.fga
#   2. Define product-specific types
#   3. Register the store via OpenFGA API at deploy time (see go-shared/authz)
